reviewText: News Reel stuff  Good but needs to be put together better.  Excellent service

See the troopers go through medical checks, get uniforms, and load on trains. Travel to camp in Naples, load ships, travel to Afrika, and get briefings. Hear Rommel speak. See combat footage. See loads of notable leaders. Lots of equipments, German, Italian, and British. Worth watching again.
Great subtitles!
I enjoy collecting videos about WWII combat footage involving the German Army and the Afrika Korps
